Class Effect

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cmu.cs.ark.sage.effects.Effect

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IntegerEffect, IntegerPairEffect, NamedEffect

    public class Effect
extends Object
implements Comparable<Effect>
    This class is used to denote a SAGE effect.

    You can inherit this class and add whatever meta data you like to it.
